Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Shinichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a famous high school detective\Nthat solved countless difficult cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day some organization forced me\Nto take a pill that shrunk me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and turned me into Conan Edogawa!\NAlthough small, my mind is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hide my identity,\Nbut I'm a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For every case,\Nthere is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blackmailed Pro Soccer Player.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan! Are you looking\Nforward to tonight's game?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soccer game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Sunday Cup finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think'll win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious! The Tokyo Spirits,\Nbecause they got Hideo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's scored goals in 17 games in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideo's good, but I like Naoki better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Naoki hurt himself\Npracticing a while back,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he won't be able to play today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the offense and defense of\NRamusu's Big Osaka team are better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need help from the\Ndetective agency, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ryoko Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I'd like you to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He suddenly disappeared,\Nand I didn't know what else to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a picture of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were seeing each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were seeing Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that\NShinichi was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's just\Na big misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's someone who looks like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake!\NI've even kissed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kissed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he told you he was working on a case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he was actually fooling\Naround with some other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, this is just a big--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live without Shinichi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I've never\Nseen you before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this girl's deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was kissing really\Nas far as you two went?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you go even farther?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer questions like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mori Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shinichi! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the new gadget I gave you\Nthis morning, the battery--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing! I'll pass\Nthe message on to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Shinichi on the phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He said he'd call Ryoko-san\Nlater so don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to see Shinichi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go to her house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi might show up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all go together,\Nand then I can teach him a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, do you, Ryoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass. I don't care about\Nsome kids' sordid love lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I will go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lock has marks on it\Nfrom being tampered with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only men's and children's shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No girls live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right. Who exactly is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where was the tea again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teapot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Akagi-san. How long\Nhave you been seeing Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As his childhood friend,\NI just have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko Akagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does she think she is,\Nignoring me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't like talking to me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I need to delve\Na little deeper into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck happened in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that this\Nis this boy's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the person with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The National Sports Stadium\Nis really livening up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the championship match\Nof the Sunday Cup continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game remains tied at 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the Tokyo Spirits\Nbe the first to score?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will it be Big Osaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with suddenly\Nswitching the TV on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she hate the idea of\Ntalking to me that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're watching soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Ryoko-san\Ninsisted on watching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Another bad kick by Hideo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is 19-year old Hideo Akagi\Nstarting to show signs of age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! That picture was of Hideo Akagi\Nfrom the Tokyo Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then Mamoru Akagi, the boy in\Nthe picture, is his little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the magazines\Nsaid that his parents died 2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that he lives with his brother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that she really\Ndoesn't live here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is she here?\NAnd why use a fake name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Hideo missed another kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really out of form today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... Why did he make\Nsuch a simple mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed almost intentional...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Don't tell me this is actually...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the gizmo the Professor\Ngave me this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my latest invention,\Nthe Mobile Boxed Lunch Fax Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Latest invention? Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he did was shove a fax machine\Ninside a boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi-san? Shinichi-san, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kidnapping, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one kidnapped was Mamoru Akagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the younger brother of Hideo Akagi,\Nwho's playing on TV right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper's demand was that\Nhe lose the game on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you were\Ngoing out with me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you wanted to get in contact\Nwith me as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that the kidnapper\Nthreatened to kill Mamoru
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you got the police\Nor any detectives involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you used\Nthe false name of Ryoko Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was because you didn't want to\Nraise suspicion from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to bring me to the Akagi home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then tell me what\Nwas really going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know he was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even come here yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, that's because\NI'm a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please write down the details\Nabout Mamoru-kun's kidnapping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fax them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?!\NThat's Shinichi on the phone, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy! Shinichi-san\Nunderstood what I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... What's she crying about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here and explain yourself, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could swear I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hearing my voice\Nfrom the other phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Shinichi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...inside this apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I found out Mamoru-chan was kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I came to make him\Nbreakfast this morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sending the kidnapper's letter\Nthat was on the table
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the letter the kidnapper\Nmade Mamoru-chan write."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bring Mamoru back to life."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange message for\Nsomeone asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran might actually be more\Ndifficult to handle than this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideo sets up the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He's kicked the ball too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he made another bad kick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Luckily,\NTakeda is there to receive it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fakes and shoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's the Hideo we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brilliant play that broke\Nthrough the opponent's defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider your brother as good as gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late! Mamoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru-kun is dead if I don't\Nfind the kidnapper soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a 3rd grader\Nthat was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he put up a real struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's unnatural for his room\Nto be this messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the {\i1}Onimaru Quest {\i0}game\Nthat came out yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kidnapped kid wouldn't\Ntake a game with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Genta and\NMitsuhiko mentioned something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero actually dies during the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And you can't beat it\Nwithout bringing him back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing him back to life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru-kun used his own name\Nfor the main character's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mamoru in that letter meant\Nthe game's main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who Mamoru, Hideo, and Ryoko are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but who's this Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Mamoru-kun's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Hideo and Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideo's good, but I like Naoki better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! Naoki Uemura, the one\Nwho joined the Spirits last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these two marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if they were the "ki" in Naoki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found out where\NMamoru-kun is, Ryoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Shinichi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, do you know a person\Nnamed Naoki Uemura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! He's Hideo's best friend.\NHe lives real close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, does he come by often\Nto play with Mamoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Naoki-san knows\Na lot about video games...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru-kun wasn't kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scratches on the front door lock\Nand the ransacked bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit did these intentionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All to make it look\Nlike a sinister kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The full message of Mamoru-kun's\Nletter probably went like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to Naoki's house so he\Ncan bring Mamoru back to life."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper tore out and used\Nonly that one part of the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then you're saying\Nthe one who took him was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The one\Nresponsible is Naoki Uemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely Mamoru-kun\Nis at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally, finally found you, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using the toilet right now,\NI can't just come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me she's not going\Nto use karate on the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ran-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi-san says he wants\Nto talk to you on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he needs to say something\Nto me, he can say it right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something important\Nthat I want only Ran to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna give me more\Nof your excuses, then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you wanna tell me, Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi just ran outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Shinichi-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going\Nto rescue Mamoru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he went\Nto Naoki-san's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoki's? Is that where\NShinichi ran off to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're showing me the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Another bad kick by Hideo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to\Nour gifted Hideo Akagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko-chan?! What is it? I'm kind of--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Can you let me in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. My girlfriend's here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want her\Nto get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru-chan! If you're there,\Nsay something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You better knock that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi! Come out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ryoko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to leave the house\Nwithout saying a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wrote you a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I finally beat the game\Nthanks to Naoki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Ryoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mamoru really alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you doing out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in big trouble if you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Hideo! Second half's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 to 1! Hideo's finally in the zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's playing like the\Nfirst half was all a ruse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideo Akagi is truly gifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gifted, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideo's got a gift,\Nwhile I'm a man of hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both his popularity and\Nsalary are higher than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet we had basically the same number\Nof goals back in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent everyday rigorously training\Nso that I could outdo him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I finally caught up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I surpassed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until he shattered my right leg\Nduring a practice match, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He intentionally\Nwent for my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was afraid that\NI had outclassed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's put me on the sideline for\N3 full months, all thanks to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible to try to surpass him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never had any\Nintentions of hurting Mamoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the match, I was going\Nto return him to his house
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then disappear somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to get back at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the game is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tokyo Spirits have won\Nthe Sunday Cup, 3 to 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our game's over too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ryoko-chan. Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them there was a kidnapping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Hideo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would you like to dedicate\Nthis victory to the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would like to dedicate it\Nto my younger brother Mamoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I really have to give\Nthis one to Naoki instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My greatest rival, Naoki Uemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After he joined the team,\NI started scoring more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon, Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't even the slightest\Nidea of what I've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but where did you hide Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\Nwe haven't seen him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to give him a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh! The cell phone's in my bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't always know it,\Nhe gave it to me today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Of all times,\Nwhy won't it open now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're there, Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away\Nthis time, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with that Ryoko girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing at her house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Nworking on a difficult case!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She was just--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! She was crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She cried when you called her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's\Ngoing on anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who wants to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come out and\Nexplain it all, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it matter to you? It's my own\Ndecision to cry if I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it when you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's not an answer! Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Agasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ran-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Shinichi,\Nhe ran off that way while blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blushing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it when you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said too much, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking, you little coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:28.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:37.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:42.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:48.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.05,0:22:58.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:12.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
